Hey,

00:07:01.300 --> 00:07:02.620
I'm just heading home.

00:07:03.260 --> 00:07:04.340
I'm not a suspect.

00:07:05.760 --> 00:07:06.620
Dr. Chen,

00:07:06.740 --> 00:07:07.580
orders from above.

