I'm broke, I can't pay you back.

00:09:15.460 --> 00:09:16.360
Besides,

00:09:16.370 --> 00:09:18.130
every police officer in the city is after me.

00:09:18.380 --> 00:09:19.490
I had no other choice

00:09:19.500 --> 00:09:20.930
